I'm after and that's black bear.

02:20.007 --> 02:21.406
This is good sign.

02:24.278 --> 02:25.878
A jackpot up here.

02:26.814 --> 02:29.448
Come here. Fish bones.

02:32.353 --> 02:35.420
What the bears do is
they'll fish in the rivers

02:35.489 --> 02:37.822
and the creeks and
once they get a fish,

02:37.892 --> 02:41.627
