03:18.532 --> 03:20.799
That's the lucky one, Java.

03:20.934 --> 03:25.938
This right here, it'll bring
home spring and summer meat.

03:26.073 --> 03:27.873
What do you think, rub
some good luck on ya?

03:30.611 --> 03:33.078
There we go.

03:33.213 --> 03:36.348
